7389 - Business Services, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > RW Health Partnership Holdings Pty Ltd designs, constructs and finances the redevelopment of The Royal Women's Hospital, located in Parkville, Victoria. The company is responsible for operating and maintaining the hospital and other facilities on the site over a 25-year period. The Royal Women's Hospital is a leading specialist hospital dedicated to improving the health of women and newborns. The hospital is a public health service. The company is based in Melbourne, Victoria.
